---
import Base from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---
<Base
  title="Now | Reuben Ingber"
  description="What Reuben Ingber is focused on right now: work, family, and hobbies."
>
  <div class="max-w-3xl">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-4 text-primary tracking-wide">NOW</h1>

    <div class="space-y-10 mt-8">
      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3 text-primary tracking-wide">FAMILY</h2>
        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
          Raising two amazing kids — getting ready to celebrate my son's 7th birthday, just took the family to Lancaster, PA, and going camping in the Catskills soon.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3 text-primary tracking-wide">HOBBIES</h2>
        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
          Photography, running/fitness, and Lego.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3 text-primary tracking-wide">WORK</h2>
        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
          I'm an Engineering Manager at Business Insider, focused on user engagement and newsroom tools.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3 text-primary tracking-wide">SIDE HUSTLE</h2>
        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
          Building a photography business — <a href="https://sessions.reubeningber.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-accent hover:underline font-semibold">sessions.reubeningber.com</a> — and the brand on Instagram, <a href="https://instagram.com/photosessionswithreuben" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-accent hover:underline font-semibold">@photosessionswithreuben</a>. Still early — shooting a few test families before opening up bookings in September.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3 text-primary tracking-wide">LEARNING</h2>
        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
          Going deep on AI from a few different angles — using it to build skills for style and fitness, building websites and apps, and finding ways it can help me work smarter.
        </p>
      </section>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-16 pt-6 border-t border-gray-200 text-sm text-secondary">
      <p>Last updated on July 13, 2026</p>
      <p>Inspired by <a href="https://sive.rs/nowff" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-accent hover:underline">sive.rs/nowff</a></p>
    </div>
  </div>
</Base>
